channel.title: [562] DieBridScape [562] - NvP, PvP, skills, SMARTNPCS! Way more
channel.description:
Hey you've probably seen my awesome 525 project. Since 562 came out and its base is so epic, I started one. Ofc it has got all basic stuff like npcs, objects, player rendering. dont ask for it.
So far I've edited:
- SMART NPC'S! THEY EAT, VENG, FARCAST, SPEC! - Banking - Mining - Woodcutting - Prayer - Skillcapes - MagicOnPlayer - Added more armour like spirit shields etc - Added more advanced specs like claws - Added player editor in server frame - Added perfect following (still no clip) - Combat system now works proper - Added special system - Fixed interface places on hd / filled screen - Changed spawn / death places - Started clipping - Fixed the picking up (you walk to it and pick up) - FIXED INVENT PACKET =] - Added more specials - Food added - Pots added (with shark-brewing, rs-like) - 100% npc cb with specs! - Command section in server frame - 90% projectiles - 90% protect from prayer - NPCs now have block anims
beta testers client uploaded. on about 5/7 For commands do the ` key under your escape key, then a space and the command panel will come up. Commands: - item - fight (brings you to a smart-npc, and starts to fight) - spec (infinite spec) - Just use mantas and sup str pots, didnt do the correct cb formula yet.
[url=http://www.mediafire.com/?irzykzxgylq]http://www.mediafire.com/?irzykzxgylq[/url]
A few pics [img]http://reddragonknights.co.uk/images/agsspec2.png[/img] [img]http://03data.com/03s/npccb.png[/img] [img]http://03data.com/03s/npccb2.png[/img] [img]http://03data.com/03s/newgui.png[/img]
Full screen HD is just epic.
